Package com.netbuilder.Presentation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminButtonListener
    This actionListener class is called when the admin button is pressed and goes through a login page
    AdminView
    This class hold the GUI that is show when the admin has logged in and is setting an atmosphere or setting off a shuffle playlist
    ClientView
    This Class contains the GUI screen for the standard user functionality (Not admin privilages)
    CoinButtonListener
    This actionListener class is called when the user pressed the coin button to add money
    GoBackListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the admin wants to go back to the clientpage.
    MouseViewListener
    This actionListener class is called when the user clicks on the search bar and clears it
    PauseButtonListener
    This actionListener class activates when the user presses the pause button
    PlayButtonListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the user presses the play button.
    PopListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the admin presses the pop atmosphere button and sets off a genre specific random playlist of pop songs and starts a new shuffle thread to play them
    RandomPlaylistListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the admin presses the random playlist shuffle button and activated the SetOffShufflePlaylist method and creates a random playlist of songs then starts a new shuffle thread to play them
    ReggaeListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the admin presses the reggae atmosphere button and sets off a genre specific random playlist of reggae songs and starts a new shuffle thread to play them
    ResultListener
    This actionListener class deals with when the user clicks on a result by adding the song selected to the playQueue
    RockListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the admin presses the rock atmosphere button and sets off a genre specific random playlist of rock songs and starts a new shuffle thread to play them
    RoundJTextField
    This class has been ripped from http://stackoverflow.com/questions/8515601/java-swing-rounded-border-for-jtextfield It makes the search bar rounded
    SearchFunctionListener
    This class will deal with all action listeners and subsequent business logic coming from text being entered to the search bar
    SkipActionListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the user presses the skip button.
    SpeechListener
    This actionListener class is activated when the admin presses the speeches atmosphere button and sets off a genre specific random playlist of speeches and starts a new shuffle thread to play them
